title: The One About Concerts
description:
This week on Sibling Rivalry Bob and Monét argue about concerts! From the magic of Monét seeing Beyoncé live to Bob's early 20s indie concert BFF to Bob and Monét announcing their tour, you won't want to miss this episode! Tune in to find out whose recently started 'getting into Michael Jackson' and what Kendrick Lamar fans are really like!
